user.bio: Beer is proof that God loves us and wants us to be happy.
Love trying new craft beer. The darker the better! "In Vino Veritas, In Cervesio Felicitas"
Beer is a simple yet meaningful way of sharing and enjoying different cultures. Also, it's super tasty.

items.checkin_comment: Interesting barrrel aged sour!  Oak notes!
Bought this last summer through Tavour.  Nice tartness woody flavors are well balanced.   Drinks way too easy for 11.6%
